# Treat Simulink/MATLAB binaries as binary (no line-ending mangling, no bad merges)
*.slx   binary
*.mdl   binary
*.mat   binary
*.mlx   binary
*.slxc  binary
*.mexw64 binary

# ── Git LFS candidates (uncomment after `git lfs install`) ──
# Large data/maps or FEA exports you MUST version:
# *.mat   filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# *.aedt  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
